data.description: ***Great income producing opportunity for investors*** Tons of potential and a great low price. This welcoming one level ranch home sits on a private, level 1/3 acre lot with a gorgeous tree line in the back! 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home features a spacious open floor plan with the perfect space for entertaining or enjoying family time. Great location in established, quaint neighborhood! Only minutes from several restaurants and shops, numerous parks, golf and Columbia State College. Outdoor enthusiasts can enjoy David Crockett State Park, Rotary Park, Laurel Hill and Natchez Trace - all nearby. Fully encapsulated crawl space. Newer hot water heater. No HOA. Great investment property or starter home - perfect for the next family! You must see this gem to truly appreciate it.
